1
00:00:02,830 --> 00:00:05,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Partway through the 21st century,</i></font>

2
00:00:05,880 --> 00:00:10,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>the mafiosi who ruled the 
underworld became "Dark Lords."</i></font>

3
00:00:12,090 --> 00:00:14,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And the bounty hunters who
would slay these Dark Lords?</i></font>

4
00:00:14,930 --> 00:00:15,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>They are known as...</i></font>

5
00:00:16,430 --> 00:00:18,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>the heroic Braves!</i></font>

6
00:00:23,120 --> 00:00:24,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Broke again.</i></font>

7
00:00:25,360 --> 00:00:29,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Dammit, if only they hadn't 
found me at that last hotel...</i></font>

8
00:00:30,240 --> 00:00:32,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If I can't find a gig before 
the end of the month,</i></font>

9
00:00:32,710 --> 00:00:34,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I won't be able to afford this room.</i></font>

10
00:00:35,600 --> 00:00:38,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Should I try and sell 
off the extra E3 I have?</i></font>

11
00:00:38,640 --> 00:00:39,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>No!</i></font>

12
00:00:38,890 --> 00:00:40,180
<font size="20">{\an8}<font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#000103"><b>Illegal</b></font></font></font>

13
00:00:41,060 --> 00:00:44,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Or I could take a hit job 
from a random Dark Lord...</i></font>

14
00:00:44,480 --> 00:00:45,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Absolutely not!</i></font>

15
00:00:44,560 --> 00:00:46,150
<font size="20">{\an8}<font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#000103"><b>Illegal</b></font></font></font>

16
00:00:51,230 --> 00:00:53,740
<font size="20">{\an8}<b><font size="10"><font color="#343435">Yashiro-san</font></font></b></font>

17
00:00:51,230 --> 00:00:53,740
<font size="20">{\an8}<b><font size="10"><font color="#343435">You coming today?</font></font></b></font>

18
00:00:56,290 --> 00:00:58,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, no sense sulking around here.</font>

19
00:00:58,570 --> 00:01:00,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Guess I'll head to Ed's 
and see what's available.</font>

20
00:01:04,290 --> 00:01:08,000
<font size="20">{\an8}<font color="#4c413a"><font face="Times New Roman"><b><font size="40">Scum of the Brave</font></b></font></font></font>

21
00:02:33,090 --> 00:02:38,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font color="#010000"><font face="Times New Roman"><b>{\an1}A Brave's Errands</b></font></font></font>

22
00:02:42,290 --> 00:02:43,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Master!</font>

23
00:02:43,260 --> 00:02:46,270
<font size="20">{\an8}<font size="40"><font color="#f9f9f9"><b>Jogamine Aki</b></font></font></font>

24
00:02:43,260 --> 00:02:46,270
<font size="20">{\an8}<font size="32"><font color="#f9f9f9"><b>Brave in Training</b></font></font></font>

25
00:02:46,670 --> 00:02:48,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why are you here?</font>

26
00:02:48,520 --> 00:02:50,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, that's so mean.</font>

27
00:02:50,770 --> 00:02:53,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not you, <i>her</i>!</font>

28
00:02:52,790 --> 00:02:54,630
<font size="20">{\an8}<font color="#ed0ee2"><b>HER</b></font></font>

29
00:02:53,220 --> 00:02:54,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I told you not to come back again!</font>

30
00:02:55,200 --> 00:02:56,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I invited her.</font>

31
00:02:56,650 --> 00:02:57,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You wanna die?!</font>

32
00:02:57,650 --> 00:03:00,650
<font size="20">{\an8}<font size="40"><font color="#eeefef"><b>Ishino the Musician</b></font></font></font>

33
00:02:57,650 --> 00:03:00,650
<font size="20">{\an8}<font size="24"><font color="#f1eff1"><b>Hobby: Recording Death Cries</b></font></font></font>

34
00:03:01,040 --> 00:03:03,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't worry, Master!</font>

35
00:03:03,460 --> 00:03:06,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your assorted harsh words 
from the other day—</font>

36
00:03:06,310 --> 00:03:07,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Go home. Leave!</font>

37
00:03:07,920 --> 00:03:09,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Flunk out already!</font>

38
00:03:09,590 --> 00:03:12,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We have accepted them all as trials!</font>

39
00:03:12,150 --> 00:03:15,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I, Jogamine, am prepared 
to come call upon you</font>

40
00:03:15,200 --> 00:03:17,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">until you accept me as your apprentice!</font>

41
00:03:18,780 --> 00:03:20,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Ignore her.</i></font>

42
00:03:20,830 --> 00:03:23,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I actually have a job for Jogamine-san,</font>

43
00:03:23,340 --> 00:03:26,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">related to her encounter with 
the Count of Amber Thorns.</font>

44
00:03:27,740 --> 00:03:29,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're actually looking into that?</font>

45
00:03:29,870 --> 00:03:32,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And I accepted, in order 
to pay my monthly tuition!</font>

46
00:03:33,130 --> 00:03:36,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Considering she can read people's minds...</i></font>

47
00:03:37,440 --> 00:03:42,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She might be able to find something 
about that weird regeneration power.</i></font>

48
00:03:45,640 --> 00:03:47,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Interested?</font>

49
00:03:47,080 --> 00:03:49,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hell no, leave me out of it.</font>

50
00:03:49,330 --> 00:03:53,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, Yashiro-san, you've been 
off your game lately.</font>

51
00:03:53,690 --> 00:03:56,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you losing your edge 
with Malta-san being gone?</font>

52
00:03:56,590 --> 00:03:59,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's rich, coming from a 
joke of a swordsman like you.</font>

53
00:03:59,230 --> 00:04:01,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Excuse me, who is Malta-san? A woman?</font>

54
00:04:01,820 --> 00:04:04,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You wanna hit up the dojo
so I can kick your ass?</font>

55
00:04:05,990 --> 00:04:08,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Unfortunately, I have a job 
that needs attending to.</font>

56
00:04:10,980 --> 00:04:13,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Could you please answer me, Master?!</font>

57
00:04:13,480 --> 00:04:15,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shut up! Go home!</font>

58
00:04:15,230 --> 00:04:16,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I will not!</font>

59
00:04:16,610 --> 00:04:17,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, Ed!</font>

60
00:04:17,980 --> 00:04:20,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Throw this noisy kid out!</font>

61
00:04:20,000 --> 00:04:21,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're noisier.</font>

62
00:04:22,000 --> 00:04:23,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And if you're not gonna 
order, go home.</font>

63
00:04:29,350 --> 00:04:30,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fine then.</font>

64
00:04:30,400 --> 00:04:33,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now, wait a second, Yashiro-san.</font>

65
00:04:33,590 --> 00:04:37,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can you serve as Jogamine-san's 
bodyguard during her investigation?</font>

66
00:04:39,550 --> 00:04:41,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why in the hell would I?</font>

67
00:04:41,540 --> 00:04:43,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For 115,000 yen.</font>

68
00:04:47,320 --> 00:04:51,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The exact amount you owe 
me after losing at cards.</font>

69
00:04:51,360 --> 00:04:54,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Since I need to do some 
shopping for this job,</font>

70
00:04:55,000 --> 00:04:58,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I really need you
to pay it back right now...</font>

71
00:04:58,520 --> 00:05:01,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then again, if you help me out with this,</font>

72
00:05:01,700 --> 00:05:04,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I suppose I could call us even...</font>

73
00:05:08,430 --> 00:05:11,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry. Don't have the cash on me.</font>

74
00:05:11,000 --> 00:05:14,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then how about some of 
your cards as collateral?</font>

75
00:05:14,080 --> 00:05:17,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Four copies of "Assault of the 
Mountain Infantry" should cover it.</font>

76
00:05:22,520 --> 00:05:23,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This blows.</font>

77
00:05:30,430 --> 00:05:32,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Master?</font>

78
00:05:37,810 --> 00:05:39,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you think of my disguise?!</font>

79
00:05:39,920 --> 00:05:42,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sara picked it out for me!</font>

80
00:05:42,400 --> 00:05:45,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, the delinquent princess?</font>

81
00:05:46,090 --> 00:05:49,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's less that she's a delinquent...</font>

82
00:05:49,060 --> 00:05:50,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, never mind.</font>

83
00:05:50,960 --> 00:05:54,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But seriously, what do you 
think of the disguise?</font>

84
00:05:56,000 --> 00:05:57,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I guess it works?</font>

85
00:05:58,510 --> 00:05:59,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Not that I care.</i></font>

86
00:06:06,850 --> 00:06:08,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you!</font>

87
00:06:08,600 --> 00:06:10,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your disguise is great too!</font>

88
00:06:10,860 --> 00:06:14,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You give off the exact impression 
of a hoodlum with no prospects!</font>

89
00:06:14,770 --> 00:06:17,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you trying to start something?</font>

90
00:06:17,670 --> 00:06:18,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, whatever.</font>

91
00:06:19,510 --> 00:06:21,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's get in there and 
take care of this, quick.</font>

92
00:06:22,000 --> 00:06:24,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right! Leave it to me!</font>

93
00:06:29,950 --> 00:06:31,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I hate working.</i></font>

94
00:06:45,070 --> 00:06:47,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Today at 9PM at a club in Shinjuku,</i></font>

95
00:06:47,900 --> 00:06:52,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Matsugi—the peeping tom—will 
provide you with some E3.</i></font>

96
00:06:53,230 --> 00:06:58,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When that happens, Jogamine-san 
will ask a certain question.</font>

97
00:06:58,020 --> 00:06:59,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What question?</font>

98
00:07:00,780 --> 00:07:04,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That is something
for you to look forward to.</font>

99
00:07:14,720 --> 00:07:19,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, you okay with using E3 
for an errand like this?</font>

100
00:07:19,440 --> 00:07:20,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes!</font>

101
00:07:20,640 --> 00:07:22,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If it's to further our mission
 of public order,</font>

102
00:07:22,820 --> 00:07:25,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">we are allowed to utilize 
it at our discretion.</font>

103
00:07:26,400 --> 00:07:27,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.</font>

104
00:07:28,140 --> 00:07:30,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And that leads to more junkies.</font>

105
00:07:30,050 --> 00:07:31,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's fine, it's fine!</font>

106
00:07:31,780 --> 00:07:33,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Everybody's doing it.</font>

107
00:07:36,100 --> 00:07:38,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Master, those people...</font>

108
00:07:38,610 --> 00:07:40,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, they're using, too.</font>

109
00:07:43,400 --> 00:07:47,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The feeling of excitement that comes 
from using E3 can become addictive.</font>

110
00:07:47,830 --> 00:07:49,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It costs an arm and a leg,</i></font>

111
00:07:49,130 --> 00:07:52,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>but there are still people 
who use it recreationally.</i></font>

112
00:07:58,000 --> 00:08:03,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, c'mon, don't stick your neck 
into unnecessary trouble.</font>

113
00:08:08,020 --> 00:08:10,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They might even be in 
the same business as us.</font>

114
00:08:11,760 --> 00:08:14,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Granted, I mostly just wanna 
get home unaccosted...</i></font>

115
00:08:16,110 --> 00:08:18,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Wait, she can hear me, right?</i></font>

116
00:08:23,310 --> 00:08:24,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's your problem?</font>

117
00:08:24,830 --> 00:08:26,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You drunk off of ginger ale?</font>

118
00:08:27,200 --> 00:08:31,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No. My ether perception...</font>

119
00:08:31,040 --> 00:08:35,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm able to sense other people's thoughts 
as they surface in their minds.</font>

120
00:08:35,880 --> 00:08:37,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But in a crowd like this...</font>

121
00:08:37,930 --> 00:08:40,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's hard to tune into a specific channel.</font>

122
00:08:43,040 --> 00:08:47,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not to worry!
I'll be fine after a bit of rest!</font>

123
00:08:48,270 --> 00:08:49,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Me, worry?</font>

124
00:08:50,960 --> 00:08:52,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You oughta read my mind.</font>

125
00:08:52,650 --> 00:08:54,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think you deserve it.</font>

126
00:08:56,280 --> 00:08:58,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You really do...</font>

127
00:08:58,590 --> 00:09:01,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're a sadist. How perverted.</font>

128
00:09:03,860 --> 00:09:05,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

129
00:09:05,660 --> 00:09:07,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's Yashiro!</font>

130
00:09:07,630 --> 00:09:10,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I heard I was meeting with a girl.</font>

131
00:09:11,880 --> 00:09:14,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, who is she? Your girlfriend?</font>

132
00:09:15,170 --> 00:09:16,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Absolutely not.</font>

133
00:09:17,530 --> 00:09:21,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, although I don't mind 
the misunderstanding!</font>

134
00:09:21,570 --> 00:09:23,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's nice to meet you.
My name is Jogamine!</font>

135
00:09:23,280 --> 00:09:24,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm Master's first—</font>

136
00:09:25,050 --> 00:09:28,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is Ishino's gofer.</font>

137
00:09:28,540 --> 00:09:31,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's <i>real</i> stupid,
so I have to babysit her.</font>

138
00:09:33,040 --> 00:09:34,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's cute.</font>

139
00:09:34,870 --> 00:09:36,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Want some candy?</font>

140
00:09:37,110 --> 00:09:38,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Candy?</font>

141
00:09:38,200 --> 00:09:41,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come on, we're in a rush.</font>

142
00:09:41,190 --> 00:09:43,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd rather we settle this
smooth and quick.</font>

143
00:09:43,970 --> 00:09:45,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure, sure.</font>

144
00:09:46,780 --> 00:09:48,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here you go. Nine doses.</font>

145
00:09:49,350 --> 00:09:51,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Indeed, it is!</font>

146
00:09:51,610 --> 00:09:52,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, also...</font>

147
00:09:53,680 --> 00:09:56,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not sure why,</font>

148
00:09:56,180 --> 00:09:59,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but Ishino-san asked me 
to ask you a question.</font>

149
00:09:59,580 --> 00:10:00,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah?</font>

150
00:10:00,330 --> 00:10:00,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure.</font>

151
00:10:01,550 --> 00:10:04,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you happen to have any E4 for sale?</font>

152
00:10:10,590 --> 00:10:12,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">E4? What's that?</font>

153
00:10:13,130 --> 00:10:14,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Some kind of codeword?</font>

154
00:10:14,800 --> 00:10:17,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I dunno. Don't ask me.</font>

155
00:10:18,020 --> 00:10:20,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In that case, it's quite all right!</font>

156
00:10:23,510 --> 00:10:25,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, I'm off.</font>

157
00:10:25,210 --> 00:10:25,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure.</font>

158
00:10:32,680 --> 00:10:36,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh... Jogamine was your name, right?</font>

159
00:10:36,690 --> 00:10:37,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes!</font>

160
00:10:37,820 --> 00:10:41,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You really should stop 
working for that four-eyes.</font>

161
00:10:46,010 --> 00:10:48,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did you read his mind just now?</font>

162
00:10:48,160 --> 00:10:50,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, perfectly.</font>

163
00:10:50,570 --> 00:10:54,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The second I posed the 
question, his animosity—</font>

164
00:10:54,000 --> 00:10:56,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">no, more like suspicion?</font>

165
00:10:56,970 --> 00:10:59,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">His suspicion of us became very strong.</font>

166
00:10:59,360 --> 00:11:02,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's hard to explain, but I think...</font>

167
00:11:02,640 --> 00:11:04,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nah, don't bother.</font>

168
00:11:05,350 --> 00:11:07,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm just here as an escort.</font>

169
00:11:07,720 --> 00:11:10,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can give Ishino all the details.</font>

170
00:11:10,810 --> 00:11:11,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right!</font>

171
00:11:12,510 --> 00:11:15,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I guess that's this job taken care of.</font>

172
00:11:16,850 --> 00:11:18,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see...</font>

173
00:11:20,450 --> 00:11:21,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then, I'll be on my way!</font>

174
00:11:22,370 --> 00:11:26,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm a bit curious about that group we 
saw before, so if you'll excuse me!</font>

175
00:11:33,440 --> 00:11:34,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey!</font>

176
00:11:36,790 --> 00:11:38,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Miss—</font>

177
00:11:38,290 --> 00:11:39,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Pardon me!</font>

178
00:11:39,590 --> 00:11:40,760
<font size="20">{\an8}<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><font size="40"><font color="#97b5ba">Toss</font></font></font></b></font>

179
00:11:46,080 --> 00:11:47,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You know her?</font>

180
00:11:47,640 --> 00:11:48,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nope.</font>

181
00:11:54,460 --> 00:11:55,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Pleased to meet you!</font>

182
00:11:55,710 --> 00:11:58,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I am a second year at the 
academy, Jogamine Aki!</font>

183
00:11:58,680 --> 00:12:02,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I sensed incredible evil, 
which led me to this place!</font>

184
00:12:02,530 --> 00:12:04,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You, the red-headed young man!</font>

185
00:12:05,280 --> 00:12:08,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You two have taken two women against 
their will and confined them here,</font>

186
00:12:08,160 --> 00:12:10,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">with the intent of administering 
illegal drugs to them,</font>

187
00:12:10,480 --> 00:12:13,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">before taking advantage of 
them in a lascivious fashion!</font>

188
00:12:13,290 --> 00:12:16,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because of my ability to 
read minds, I know all this!</font>

189
00:12:16,710 --> 00:12:19,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Release the two of them right now!</font>

190
00:12:19,300 --> 00:12:20,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you don't,</font>

191
00:12:20,880 --> 00:12:24,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">then in the name of the academy, 
I will serve you justice!</font>

192
00:12:26,910 --> 00:12:29,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, no. Nah, nah, nah, nah, nah.</font>

193
00:12:30,220 --> 00:12:32,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've gotta be drunk.</font>

194
00:12:32,460 --> 00:12:35,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We were doing no such thing.</font>

195
00:12:35,520 --> 00:12:38,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You know you're not supposed 
to mix drinks and E3, right?</font>

196
00:12:40,670 --> 00:12:42,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see!</font>

197
00:12:42,040 --> 00:12:46,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Still, it's inconceivable that 
I'd be drunk! After all...</font>

198
00:12:48,560 --> 00:12:52,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's illegal for minors to drink!</font>

199
00:12:52,760 --> 00:12:54,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Get over here.</font>

200
00:12:58,430 --> 00:12:59,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Listen, you...</font>

201
00:12:59,900 --> 00:13:02,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, I'm sorry!</font>

202
00:13:02,000 --> 00:13:03,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was a somewhat urgent matter,</font>

203
00:13:03,800 --> 00:13:06,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so I decided that I should 
take action immediately!</font>

204
00:13:09,010 --> 00:13:12,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Braves are professional killers, not cops.</i></font>

205
00:13:13,280 --> 00:13:17,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm not getting involved in this kind 
of mess when it's not even for a job.</i></font>

206
00:13:17,490 --> 00:13:20,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Is this really the kind of situation 
you should stick your nose into?</i></font>

207
00:13:20,800 --> 00:13:21,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Master!</font>

208
00:13:23,700 --> 00:13:27,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They want help.</font>

209
00:13:34,520 --> 00:13:36,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I was right after all.</i></font>

210
00:13:36,980 --> 00:13:40,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Should've known a gig from 
Ishino the Musician...</i></font>

211
00:13:40,840 --> 00:13:43,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>couldn't end without some trouble.</i></font>

212
00:13:47,010 --> 00:13:52,010
<font size="20">{\an8}<font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#f1f1f1"><b><font size="28">Scum of the Brave</font></b></font></font></font>

213
00:13:55,840 --> 00:13:57,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, Sahara.</font>

214
00:13:57,500 --> 00:14:00,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who're these psychos?</font>

215
00:14:00,020 --> 00:14:01,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did you pull something?</font>

216
00:14:02,780 --> 00:14:04,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're just some Braves passing through.</font>

217
00:14:04,860 --> 00:14:06,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Braves?</font>

218
00:14:06,370 --> 00:14:10,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't think I've ever seen 
a for-real Brave before.</font>

219
00:14:10,000 --> 00:14:12,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What, am I not for-real enough for you?</font>

220
00:14:14,970 --> 00:14:16,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's your name, mister?</font>

221
00:14:16,960 --> 00:14:19,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Malta. Malta the Mole.</font>

222
00:14:23,100 --> 00:14:24,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're lying.</font>

223
00:14:24,420 --> 00:14:26,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This stuff about you being 
a Brave is real,</font>

224
00:14:26,990 --> 00:14:28,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but that's not your name.</font>

225
00:14:28,910 --> 00:14:30,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can tell with stuff like that.</font>

226
00:14:30,930 --> 00:14:32,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's telling the truth!</font>

227
00:14:32,730 --> 00:14:34,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Apparently he can read people's impulses?</font>

228
00:14:34,690 --> 00:14:36,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Or emotional signals, perhaps.</font>

229
00:14:36,880 --> 00:14:40,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's able to perceive that 
information as colors.</font>

230
00:14:42,170 --> 00:14:44,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You could've mentioned that sooner!</font>

231
00:14:45,000 --> 00:14:46,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's your real name?</font>

232
00:14:48,480 --> 00:14:51,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yashiro. Yashiro the Reaper.</font>

233
00:14:53,520 --> 00:14:54,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For real?</font>

234
00:14:54,910 --> 00:14:55,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Looks like it.</font>

235
00:14:56,250 --> 00:14:59,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, this guy is who the 
Coffin Count's after...</font>

236
00:15:02,980 --> 00:15:05,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What about you? This your place?</font>

237
00:15:06,320 --> 00:15:07,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nope.</font>

238
00:15:07,990 --> 00:15:10,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I'm friends with the owner.</font>

239
00:15:10,650 --> 00:15:12,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah?</font>

240
00:15:12,010 --> 00:15:14,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And is that friend of yours a Dark Lord?</font>

241
00:15:15,970 --> 00:15:16,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No.</font>

242
00:15:17,400 --> 00:15:21,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But he's acquaintances with a
Dark Lord who deals illegal drugs...</font>

243
00:15:21,010 --> 00:15:25,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Or, rather, a woman who is the 
minion of said Dark Lord.</font>

244
00:15:26,190 --> 00:15:28,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The... Verdigris Quarter?</font>

245
00:15:29,310 --> 00:15:31,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's what she goes by.</font>

246
00:15:32,970 --> 00:15:35,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay. Stop. Don't read anything else.</font>

247
00:15:35,400 --> 00:15:36,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, sir!</font>

248
00:15:37,430 --> 00:15:39,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You boys have two options.</font>

249
00:15:40,140 --> 00:15:42,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can try and kill us right now.</font>

250
00:15:43,400 --> 00:15:45,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Or you can hand those two over.</font>

251
00:15:48,000 --> 00:15:49,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't get it.</font>

252
00:15:49,710 --> 00:15:52,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why are you working
with an academy student?</font>

253
00:15:52,710 --> 00:15:54,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do I need to explain myself?</font>

254
00:15:54,930 --> 00:15:57,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was really hoping we 
could do this peacefully.</font>

255
00:15:57,350 --> 00:15:58,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's right!</font>

256
00:15:58,790 --> 00:16:02,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Master would rather go home 
without any more work!</font>

257
00:16:02,550 --> 00:16:07,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But he's willing to strike you down 
if it means saving the others!</font>

258
00:16:10,850 --> 00:16:14,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah... personally speaking, I think...</font>

259
00:16:15,380 --> 00:16:17,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It'd be boring to just let them go,</font>

260
00:16:17,750 --> 00:16:20,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so since we're both pros here, 
how about a one-on-one duel?</font>

261
00:16:20,810 --> 00:16:22,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ether perception use is allowed.</font>

262
00:16:22,880 --> 00:16:24,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can lose via surrender.</font>

263
00:16:24,750 --> 00:16:27,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And neither side reveals their power.</font>

264
00:16:29,010 --> 00:16:29,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How about it?</font>

265
00:16:33,260 --> 00:16:36,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay. I'm sure you'd rather keep 
your rep intact, after all.</font>

266
00:16:37,520 --> 00:16:38,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My rep?</font>

267
00:16:39,700 --> 00:16:42,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm a little offended you make 
it sound so... professional.</font>

268
00:16:43,490 --> 00:16:46,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All I really care about 
is having a good time.</font>

269
00:16:51,200 --> 00:16:51,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Master—</font>

270
00:16:51,940 --> 00:16:53,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not a word.</font>

271
00:16:53,720 --> 00:16:56,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's not lying, right?</font>

272
00:16:56,160 --> 00:16:59,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He... isn't. But...</font>

273
00:17:01,160 --> 00:17:03,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's all I need to know.</font>

274
00:17:07,790 --> 00:17:12,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He probably understands the 
nature of my ether perception.</i></font>

275
00:17:16,370 --> 00:17:20,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Considering that he decided to change our 
confrontation into something like this...</i></font>

276
00:17:20,530 --> 00:17:25,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, let's be...gin...</font>

277
00:17:30,140 --> 00:17:31,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Control of an invisible weapon.</i></font>

278
00:17:31,860 --> 00:17:33,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That's his power.</i></font>

279
00:17:35,040 --> 00:17:37,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>From his stance, it's probably a katana.</i></font>

280
00:17:37,660 --> 00:17:40,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>There's a chance its
length can change, too.</i></font>

281
00:17:40,560 --> 00:17:42,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Dodging isn't gonna get me much.</i></font>

282
00:17:43,690 --> 00:17:47,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But at this range, if I step 
in with full strength...</i></font>

283
00:18:12,600 --> 00:18:13,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wanna keep going?</font>

284
00:18:14,380 --> 00:18:16,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nah. I surrender.</font>

285
00:18:19,780 --> 00:18:21,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cool, cool!</font>

286
00:18:21,970 --> 00:18:24,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're strong, Yashiro the Reaper.</font>

287
00:18:24,400 --> 00:18:26,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wanna come work for our boss?</font>

288
00:18:28,360 --> 00:18:29,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's go.</font>

289
00:18:29,530 --> 00:18:30,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right!</font>

290
00:18:42,140 --> 00:18:44,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Their parents are on the 
way to pick them up.</font>

291
00:18:44,990 --> 00:18:46,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Isn't that great?!</font>

292
00:18:46,690 --> 00:18:47,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not at all.</font>

293
00:18:48,140 --> 00:18:50,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Those pains in the ass
know who I am now.</font>

294
00:18:50,760 --> 00:18:51,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What a nuisance.</font>

295
00:18:52,230 --> 00:18:54,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes! And I appreciate your 
assistance in spite of that!</font>

296
00:18:59,410 --> 00:19:01,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why a Brave?</font>

297
00:19:01,440 --> 00:19:02,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Excuse me?</font>

298
00:19:02,360 --> 00:19:04,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You could've picked another 
way to help people.</font>

299
00:19:05,820 --> 00:19:07,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Like being a cop...</font>

300
00:19:07,890 --> 00:19:09,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Or a firefighter.</font>

301
00:19:13,030 --> 00:19:16,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fair enough. I think in 
my case, it boils down...</font>

302
00:19:17,490 --> 00:19:19,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">to the fact that my father was Brave.</font>

303
00:19:22,990 --> 00:19:26,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He died before I enrolled at the academy,</font>

304
00:19:26,650 --> 00:19:31,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but he used to speak to me of 
the ideals he held as a Brave.</font>

305
00:19:33,680 --> 00:19:38,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And so, my dream is to follow in his 
footsteps and become a great Brave!</font>

306
00:19:39,300 --> 00:19:41,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your old man...</font>

307
00:19:42,390 --> 00:19:44,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Must've been a decent guy.</font>

308
00:19:46,340 --> 00:19:47,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's right!</font>

309
00:19:51,470 --> 00:19:54,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Only the lowest kind
of scum become Braves.</i></font>

310
00:19:56,140 --> 00:19:58,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The good ones all die.</i></font>

311
00:19:59,850 --> 00:20:01,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't walk so close to me!</font>

312
00:20:01,310 --> 00:20:02,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But why not?!</font>

313
00:20:02,710 --> 00:20:03,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">'Cause you're obnoxious.</font>

314
00:20:03,770 --> 00:20:05,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you embarrassed?</font>

315
00:20:12,050 --> 00:20:14,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But you escorted her back 
to the dorm, didn't you?</i></font>

316
00:20:14,870 --> 00:20:17,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're so diligent, Yashiro-san.</font>

317
00:20:17,630 --> 00:20:20,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As a freelancer, you should really 
try and enjoy your work more.</font>

318
00:20:22,080 --> 00:20:24,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hearing that from you freaks me out, man.</font>

319
00:20:25,290 --> 00:20:27,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And don't call her to the 
bar anymore, seriously.</font>

320
00:20:28,480 --> 00:20:29,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Are you worried about her?</i></font>

321
00:20:29,740 --> 00:20:31,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's not like that.</font>

322
00:20:31,410 --> 00:20:33,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's just in the way.</font>

323
00:20:34,910 --> 00:20:38,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Still, I don't think
she's going to give up.</font>

324
00:20:38,570 --> 00:20:40,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did she happen to tell you?</font>

325
00:20:40,480 --> 00:20:42,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">About who her father is...</font>

326
00:20:42,630 --> 00:20:43,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Don't.</i></font>

327
00:20:44,720 --> 00:20:45,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't care.</font>

328
00:20:46,640 --> 00:20:48,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>My chicken's getting cold. 
I'm hanging up.</i></font>

